"{\"uid\": \"russian-sports.ru-en-will-russia-go-to-the-olympics.html\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Take part in the mass poll \\\"Will Russia go to the Olympics?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 59, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.8868656385948841, \"rank\": 0.12235937739030044, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 5, \"to\": 9}, {\"ngram\": \"the mass poll\", \"from\": 13, \"to\": 26}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 46, \"to\": 58}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\".You can vote until July 1, 2024 and you can do it once from one internet device.\", \"from\": 59, \"to\": 141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \".You\", \"from\": 60, \"to\": 64}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 80, \"to\": 84}, {\"ngram\": \"one internet device\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is not much time left before the start of the2024 Olympics, but the debate in the sports community is not subsiding.\", \"from\": 143, \"to\": 265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"much time\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 165}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 187}, {\"ngram\": \"the2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 207}, {\"ngram\": \"the debate\", \"from\": 213, \"to\": 223}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports community\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some believe that Russia should participate in the Games, while others express the opposite opinion: \\\"participation of our national team under discriminatory conditions is unacceptable.\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.8868656385948841, \"rank\": 0.12235937739030044, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://d